verse = \lyricmode {
  Lo, as an ea -- gle, hov -- 'ring o'er its young
when it has thrust them from its eye -- rie,
will catch them, bear -- ing them a -- long
on out -- spread wings that nev -- er wea -- ry,
so was the LORD then Ja -- cob's guide:
no for -- eign god was at his side.
He made him ride on lof -- ty moun -- tains,
fed him on har -- vests of the field.
From crags flowed hon -- ey as from foun -- tains;
the flin -- ty rock its oil did yield.
}
